title: 100 x LuxLiv® Plastic Sandwich & Pen – Premium Zip Food Storage – Lunch & Snack Ziplock – 7x8-inch Freezer – Non-BPA & Reusable
features: FREE PEN: Each packs includes a free permanent marker in black ink to allow you to easily write any message or notes you wish directly onto the sandwich bags!
100 BAGS: Each pack contains 100 premium quality sandwich bags!

DURABLE DESIGN: LuxLiv lunch bags are made of plastic. This durable and resilient material will not tear or break easily so you can carry your sandwich and snacks safely and efficiently. The food bags are transparent so you can quickly spot what’s inside. The sandwich bags are completely free of toxins and BPA for enhanced safety!

MULTIPURPOSE: Although great for sandwiches and snacks, our transparent lunch bags can also be used to store leftovers, veggies, smoothie mixes, meat, and fish. They are freezer-safe and reusable for more practicality!

FOR YOU AND THE KIDS: These resealable food bags are great for the family’s lunch at school or work. Use these versatile zip freezer bags to pack your kid’s sandwich and a little snack that he can enjoy on a break!

LEAKPROOF DESIGN: The LuxLiv small sandwich bags have an air-tight ziplock closure that seals in the flavours for a better experience. The lunch bags retain freshness and prevent odours so you can enjoy garlic or fish for lunch without worrying about the smell.
